.DS_Store

# ── RE generated outputs ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Timestamped run outputs from REwww (PROJECT.YYYYMMDD-HHMMSS.TYPE.EXT).
# This is deliberately specific so that named reference runs (e.g.
# PROJECT.hand.sets.xml, PROJECT.standard.coverage.xml) are kept.
*.[0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9]-[0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9].*

